Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
Good morning all.  
Pirate wants to support the NN network. 
Last year I personally considered running but was hesitant and did not trust my technical ability, so instead I just ran a handful of Giveaways and raffles of my and community donated funds to those who supported the dICOs.  
This year, I have been a proponent of KMD, worked with other projects to bring light and awareness to the people.  I have been changing thought leaders minds on KMD and the whole project.   As you may know, there were many in the community who were not happy about the inception of KMD... but those people are being talked to weekly/monthly by myself when discussing Pirate and KMD ecosystem. 

This year, we are running on a platform of Privacy, z address adoption/usage and ecosystem support.  
Attached is our preliminary distribution ideas for Notary Node income.  
TBH, I probably won't see shit... I hope Lynch is compensated appropriately for his time and management. 

The main purpose is to keep supporting KMD, it's ecosystem, those who helped with the foundation of pirate and to give back to the community as we have been with Plugins, tipbots and so on.

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content: https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/508950199553490947/552228941037961266/nn_accounts.png?width=576&height=677

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
The above are estimates/ideas.  
We will be running for 2 nodes this year.

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
I am very humble to even be considering this and Pirate is looking forward to continuing the support of the KMD ecosystem and it's projects.
Hopefully you guys don't think I am a Mushroom üòÉ

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
Pirate was released unto the wild at 16000 sats.  
It's only 100% logical that all the KMD growth since then is due to Pirate. 

:troll:

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content:
Simple.
Nothing to do with CC's or Games or Sapling.  Not at all 

:troll_hardcore:

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content: There are more platform ideas and announcements to make as we move forward but we hope to show the KMD ecosystem and the crypto world that Pirate means business and supports KMD 100%.

Author: Audo#5667
Content:
Yeah, we should build it with future in mind. A lot of the info can be reused in future elections. Perhaps the site could also list all active notaries.

This project is best kept separate from our main domain as for example we got the rebrand coming and a new site.

Regarding static page vs wordpress... honestly I'm not the best persont to judge which route to take. My understanding is that it's easier to update content to a WP site than to a staic one, and we probably have to keep iterating the content on this page especially if we reuse it in 2020.
